title: datastore
extract: Google Cloud Datastore is a NoSQL document database built for automatic scaling, high performance, and ease of application development. Cloud Datastore features include: Atomic transactions. Cloud Datastore can execute a set of operations where either all succeed, or none occur.Oct 18, 2018
